text: Aytugan () is a rural locality (a village) in Meleuzovsky Selsoviet, Meleuzovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 107 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 8 km from Meleuz, 15 km from Karan. == References == Category:Rural localities in Meleuzovsky District
title: Aytugan, Meleuzovsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
